captor.modelsystem.config
Class GUIHiddenConfig

java.lang.Object
  java.util.Observable
      captor.modelsystem.config.GUIHiddenConfig

public class GUIHiddenConfig
extends java.util.Observable

This class holds information about the state of the window like current x and y position, if the window is maximized, panel divider position and other stuffs that improve the tool usability.
